<section class="sec" style="background:var(--gray-bg)">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="about-hero-grid">
      <div class="fade">
        <div class="sec-hd"><div class="eyebrow">About SHRC</div><h2 class="sec-title">Who We Are</h2></div>
        <div class="about-body">
          <p>Founded in 1990 by Dr. Mohamad Halimi, the Saad Halimi Rehabilitation Center has served patients across Tripoli and North Lebanon for over three decades.</p>
          <p>Our purpose is to help you continue participating in your daily activities and life roles. We design treatment programs based on both the findings of our evaluation and your personal goals, because movement and function matter to every aspect of your life.</p>
          <p>We provide therapeutic treatment wherever movement and function are threatened by aging, injury, disease, or environmental factors. Our goal is always to improve your quality of life.</p>
          <p>SHRC is fully equipped with state-of-the-art rehabilitation and preventive technology, combining Western evidence-based medicine with effective Eastern therapeutic traditions for a truly integrative approach to care.</p>
          <p>Dr. Saad M. Halimi brought a new vision by redefining rehabilitation through Complementary and Alternative Medicine (CAM). This evidence-based practice combines physiotherapy, osteopathy, and acupuncture, and has been gaining international recognition for its effectiveness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-list fade" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <div class="cred"><div class="cred-name">Founded 1990</div><div class="cred-detail">Over 35 years of serving patients in Tripoli and North Lebanon.</div></div>
        <div class="cred"><div class="cred-name">HUMAC NORM Technology</div><div class="cred-detail">The gold standard in isokinetic testing and rehabilitation, quantifying progress with precision before and after every treatment course.</div></div>
        <div class="cred"><div class="cred-name">Integrative Approach</div><div class="cred-detail">Western physiotherapy combined with osteopathy, acupuncture, and complementary medicine for complete care.</div></div>
        <div class="cred"><div class="cred-name">International Recognition</div><div class="cred-detail">Collaboration with Harvard Vanguard, CSMi at Massachusetts General Hospital, and Tianjin TCM University.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

